  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>For breakfast there is a very plentiful buffet with cooked and continental options, and is served from 6.30am to 10.00am Monday to Friday, and 07.00am to 11.00am Saturday and Sunday.</p>
<p>Complimentary coffee is available in the lobby.</p>
<p>If you wish to enjoy lunch or an evening meal in the hotel restaurant Egon (adjacent to the hotel), this is bookable and payable locally. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
