  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Thon Hotel Bristol makes a great choice for anyone looking for a centrally located hotel in Bergen.</p>
<h2>A short stroll from all Bergen has to offer</h2>
<p>You’re not far from some of Bergen’s key spots when you stay here. You can stroll to the popular Bryggen Wharf, or if you’re looking to head out on a day trip then the train station is about a 10 minute walk away. You’re also just around the corner from Lille Lungegaardsvannet lake, it’s only small but it’s really lovely and has plenty of museums and galleries surrounding it as well as flowers, trees and grassy areas to lounge.</p>
<h2>Inviting, cosy rooms</h2>
<p>Rooms are cosy, with a modern feel and often have statement wallpaper to give it a homely touch. When it comes to breakfast here, it's served buffet style and there's plenty of choice on offer, so after you've tucked into some tasty food, you'll be ready to head out for a full day of exploring.</p>]]></description>
